title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
Welcome to my blog !
I am a R trainer and developer at ThinkR. I used to have a blog a few years ago, based on Hugo (in French only).
I have decided to give a try to Quarto Websites. This new site aims at sharing my thoughts and knowledge about R, data science, epidemiology-related stuff.
Some of my posts are also available in ThinkR websites :

Rtask website - English and French
ThinkR website - French
